data.description: Looking for a home in the Joliet area where you can simply move in, unpack and relax? This beautiful home is full of stylish renovations done within the last 3 months. It has been completely refurbished from floor to ceiling. As you enter the home, you are met with brand new flooring and fresh paint throughout. Guests will enjoy gathering in the open concept kitchen. The remodeled kitchen showcases new cabinets and quartz countertops. Equipped with 2022 Samsung stainless steel appliances. The welcoming family room provides ample space for gatherings or a relaxing night in. Each of the 3 spacious bedrooms has brand new carpet. Other noteworthy features: 2022 AC; new garage door; and Deep 2.5 car garage. Minutes away from the highly rated elementary and middle school as well as I-55 & I-80. Full asking price offer includes $1,000 credit for washer & dryer. Welcome Home!
